This is how to how_many_times of string and substring:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that limit is sum of (diff of string's length and substring's length) and 1

   When substring's length is more than string's length, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when

   Do this limit times:
      Remember that matches is yes
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this substring's length times:
         When item (sum of i and j) in string is not item j in substring, then:
            Remember that matches is no
            Leave the loop
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      When matches is yes, then:
         Increase count
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is count
Now you know